OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCaerphilly cheese          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fproduction returns to      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhometown                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Caerphilly cheese is once again being  
OL,6, made in its home town almost 30 years  
OL,7, after it was forced to stop.           
OL,9,FProduction of the world-famous cheese  
OL,10,Fin Caerphilly ended in 1995 when       
OL,11,FEuropean legislation made it illegal to
OL,12,Ftake delivery of unpasteurised milk in 
OL,13,Fmetal churns.                          
OL,15,FNow, Huw Rowlands, 26, and Deian       
OL,16,FThomas, 39, are hoping to reignite the 
OL,17,Flocal cheese-making tradition.         
OL,19,FThey have been working for over three  
OL,20,Fyears to perfect the cheese.           
